      <h4>3.) Local browser settings</h4>
      You can edit the local browser settings on the fly in the footer of the kreXX output. They are stored in a cookie, and only affect your current browser. Unlike the configuration file, not all settings can be edited there.<br />
      Local browser settings overwrite configuration file settings.<br />
      <b>Please note, that these are only local settings, only affecting your current browser.</b>
